69|language=Danish|publisher=[[IFPI Denmark]]|accessdate=24 April 2019}}</ref>\n* MC: 5\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"cria\"/>\n* RIAA: 5\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"riaa.com\"/>\n* RMNZ: Platinum<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=single|artist=Sam Smith|title=Too Good at Goodbyes|recent=website|id=4416|accessdate=17 November 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''The Thrill of It All''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[One Last Song]]\"\n| 27 || 94 || 66 || \u2015 || \u2015 || 36 || \u2014 || \u2015{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"One Last Song\" did not enter the [[Official New Zealand Music Chart|NZ Top 40 Singles Chart]], but peaked at number two on the NZ Heatseeker Singles Chart.<ref name=\"NZ 13 November\">{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/singles?chart=4415|title=NZ Heatseeker Singles Chart|publisher=[[Recorded Music NZ]]|date=13 November 2017|accessdate=10 November 2017}}</ref>}} || 46 || \u2015{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"One Last Song\" did not enter the ''Billboard'' Hot 100, but peaked at number eight on the Bubbling Under Hot 100 Singles chart.<ref name=\"US-Bubbling-singles\"/>}}\n| \n* BPI: Silver<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* ARIA: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.aria.com.au/pages/SinglesAccreds2018.htm|title=ARIA Charts \u2013 Accreditations \u2013 2018 Singles|publisher=Australian Recording Industry Association|accessdate=24 November 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Pray (Sam Smith song)#Remix featuring Logic|Pray]]\"<br/>{{small|(featuring [[Logic (musician)|Logic]])}}\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2018\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 ||  \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Pray\" featuring Logic did not enter the [[Mega Charts|Netherlands Top 100 Singles Chart]], but peaked at number 19 on the Netherlands Single Tip chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dutchcharts.nl/weekchart.asp?cat=st&year=2018&date=20180512|title=Dutchcharts.nl \u2013 Dutch Single Tip \u2013 12/05/2018|language=Dutch|publisher=[[MegaCharts]]|accessdate=May 12, 2018}}</re